<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id795a7a05-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s1685"><num value="1685">§ 1685.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall issue such regulations as the Secretary deems necessary to implement the provisions of this subchapter.</p>
