<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id795a7a09-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1981-10-01">Oct. 1, 1981</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/96/554/s9">section 9 of Pub. L. 96–554</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s1681">section 1681 of this title</ref>.</p>
